---
import MemberLayout from '../../layouts/MemberLayout.astro';
---

<MemberLayout title="Members Handbook">
  <div class="handbook-page">
    <div class="handbook-intro">
      <p>Welcome to the Alnmouth Village Golf Club Members Handbook. Here you'll find important information about club rules, etiquette, and course guidelines.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="handbook-sections">
      <section class="handbook-section">
        <h2>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/>
          </svg>
          General Rules
        </h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <ul>
            <li>Members must carry a valid membership card at all times when on the course</li>
            <li>Appropriate golf attire must be worn at all times on the course and in the clubhouse</li>
            <li>Mobile phones should be on silent and calls taken away from playing areas</li>
            <li>Members should report to the Clubhouse before playing</li>
            <li>Buggies must remain on designated paths and away from greens and tees</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="handbook-section">
        <h2>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
          Pace of Play
        </h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <ul>
            <li>A round of 18 holes should be completed in no more than 4 hours</li>
            <li>Keep up with the group ahead, not just ahead of the group behind</li>
            <li>If your group falls behind, invite the following group to play through</li>
            <li>Be ready to play when it's your turn - limit practice swings</li>
            <li>Leave the putting green promptly after holing out</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="handbook-section">
        <h2>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
          Course Care
        </h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <ul>
            <li>Repair all pitch marks on greens</li>
            <li>Replace or fill all divots on fairways and tees</li>
            <li>Rake bunkers after use, leaving the rake inside the bunker</li>
            <li>Do not take trolleys or bags onto greens or tees</li>
            <li>Keep trolleys and buggies at least 10 yards from greens</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="handbook-section">
        <h2>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
          Guest Policy
        </h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <ul>
            <li>Members may introduce visitors subject to green fee payment</li>
            <li>The introducing member is responsible for their guest's conduct</li>
            <li>Visitors should be booked through the Clubhouse or BRS Golf</li>
            <li>Members should accompany their guests when possible</li>
            <li>Visitors must adhere to all club rules and dress code</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="handbook-section">
        <h2>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/>
            <path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/>
            <line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/>
          </svg>
          Clubhouse & Catering
        </h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <ul>
            <li>Smart casual dress code applies in the clubhouse</li>
            <li>Golf shoes with soft spikes only are permitted</li>
            <li>Food and beverages may only be consumed in designated areas</li>
            <li>The bar is available to members and their guests</li>
            <li>Outside food and drink are not permitted in the clubhouse</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="handbook-section">
        <h2>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/>
            <path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/>
            <path d="M4 22h16"/>
            <path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"/>
            <path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"/>
            <path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/>
          </svg>
          Competitions
        </h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <ul>
            <li>Competition entry is via BRS Golf or the Clubhouse</li>
            <li>Handicaps are managed through the WHS system</li>
            <li>Cards must be returned within 24 hours of completion</li>
            <li>No-shows without notification may result in competition bans</li>
            <li>Prize presentations are held in the clubhouse after competitions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="handbook-footer">
      <p>For any queries about club rules or policies, please contact the club office or speak to a committee member.</p>
      <a href="mailto:Manager@AlnmouthVillage.Golf" class="btn btn-secondary">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
          <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
        </svg>
        Contact the Club
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .handbook-page {
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .handbook-intro {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .handbook-intro p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .handbook-sections {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .handbook-section {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .handbook-section h2 {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .handbook-section h2 svg {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .section-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-content ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .section-content li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .section-content li:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-content li::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0.5rem;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .handbook-footer {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .handbook-footer p {
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--primary);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn-secondary svg {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-light);
    }
  </style>
</MemberLayout>
